Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\pos(318,325)}櫻飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「龍槍」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人所愛 被城鎮所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼光？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚六老爺子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「龍槍」的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 那是町長發出的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「龍槍」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以辦到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒我就意味著把我送到那個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是銀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.44,0:03:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的同伴很在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妳在努力 但是能送歸我的傢伙卻在發神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這身體裡已經沒有留有銀了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有留有了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得礙事 就請他出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說會相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白 秋名 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在看著你準備怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作為比泉的後人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做出殘酷的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼神在動搖哦 比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要送歸我嗎 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量使用過多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實體化物體的力量在減弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用潤喉糖也到極限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:07:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾 美妙的世界連一瞬也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣男人不合我胃口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺言就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管問幾次 答案都一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在櫻花飛舞中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.38,0:07:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡多管閒事的同伴是很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終歸對人類是不可能把道理講清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為了小姐 也有不可讓步的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是個無聊的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因櫻花開放 所以處於瀕死狀態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一生都不能賞花 真是不幸的身體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個城鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你也並沒有什麼怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要怨恨就去怨恨比泉家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我送去那個世界的比泉家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個城鎮變成妖怪的世界 你到底怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉家只留下順從於人類的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了偽善的城鎮 是用強硬的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這次由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來建立妖怪的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有礙事的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與虛偽的城鎮一起消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.45,0:09:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的土地神真是壞心眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好打一場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經極限了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬朝這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就寄希望於她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮櫻花盡染
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類世界的完結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很美妙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會讓這種事情得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言靈也已經到極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試接觸一下影子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會變成完全的妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得把你們收拾之後了 理想的世界就只差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「龍槍」的力量變大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.93,0:11:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 是阻止不了櫻花開放的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要打倒向櫻花輸送妖力的你就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有比泉的技能？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你 把円神送歸到那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的共同意願 怎麼能和我的執念相比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被騙 被背叛 被送到那個世界的妖怪的心情是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼可能會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳作為這個偽善城鎮的頭頭 怎麼可能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這個城鎮是建立在你的犧牲上才得以建成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個城鎮裡的居民並沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.64,0:12:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們的執念不一樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.62,0:12:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組合招式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪和人類一樣可以合的來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候円神大人拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是靠著對人類的怨恨才活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此也是對我伸出拯救之手的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被拉入了黑暗中而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是那最初的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他吸引是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來的及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.10,0:13:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在円神大人的理想世界上賭上了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會照亮我的未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會後悔的 那才是正確的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再睜開眼之時 櫻花會美麗的開放著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是相遇的時機不同 就變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他只是個軟弱的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為軟弱 所以逃到未知裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的龍的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吧 痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.55,0:15:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好體會我的悔恨 我的絕望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回應大地的憤怒而顯現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起伏如觸及波瀾般驚艷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是龍脈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「龍槍」逆鱗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人所愛 被城鎮所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被龍所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終之段『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 櫻花被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花…『七鄉』被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…我們要保護城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了 円神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要把我送到那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉！！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『調率』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮…能保護好大家的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮…靠你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是櫻真町廣播
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因落下的花瓣 路變得很滑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家和睦共處 共同清掃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有我這邊屋頂被打掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳得去和蜥蜴說說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且花瓣都把藍布壓到頭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落的時候很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且賞花用的藍布是用來鋪地上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這用來當頂棚不奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是城鎮修復前的考驗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍耐 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『空調』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連著的不是室外機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不是沒有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫町長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉燒面超標100卡路里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然應該點豆芽蕎麥的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就要運動的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃華也是 這樣就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 樹裡說可以多吃點的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花的花瓣還有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會掃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個會失去平衡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天落下的找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著修復了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 長了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的報告書你還沒有交哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
